---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 - Lost in Space</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>(✖﹏✖)</h1>

      <p>
        Whoops, you're lost in space! <br />This page doesn't exist.
